  "texts": [
    "It has also become a popular spot for a marketplace where advertisers can promote their products.",
    "Due to the variety and diversity of content on this platform, users get recommendations for versatile items.",
    "In the study, we recruited Facebook users and asked them semi-structured interview questions.",
    "The interview participants were recruited using Facebook groups and word of mouth.",
    "The participants were regular Facebook users in daily life."
